title: 1985-96 Engine Torque Specs
author: Brian Bradburn
content:
The original source for this (http://torquespecs.tripod.com/su85-96.htm), as of 8/2018 is akin to malware. The ads bring back to the early 2000s in all of the worst ways, just use the PDFs I made and save yourself the aggravation. Some images were missing when I archived the pages.
